and people of Japanese descent.</i>

45
00:03:20,967 --> 00:03:25,205
<i>Bi Shonen take part in the festival
as an idol group from Japan.</i>

46
00:03:25,538 --> 00:03:29,209
<i>They are scheduled to perform
on two stages.</i>

47
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:35,582
Is this what it's like to be in a parade?

48
00:03:36,482 --> 00:03:39,519
{\an8}We could never do this in Japan.

49
00:03:39,886 --> 00:03:41,821
{\an8}It feels awesome.

50
